subject: Update JAVA version and and existing libraries
description: As a user, I want to update my application to use the latest version of the tech stack so that get rid of security vulnerabilities.

subject: Import details to dashboard via JSON files
description: As a user, I need to import existing project information using json files so that I could see all the information on the dashboard

subject: Updating spellings and case of variables and strings
description:
As a user, I want code to be refactored so that it follows prescribed standards.
Hint: Refactor variables and method name to camelCase and correct spellings if any

subject: Persist the state of the tool
description: As a user, I want to save the state of the tool when exited. So that i can return to the same state of the project.

subject: Make use of tab for completing the command in CLI
description: As a user, I want to make use of "tab" so that it would be easy for completing the command in cli

subject: Make use to shortcuts in commands
description: As a user, I want it to flexible to use shortcuts so that  most of spelling mistakes can be avoided

subject: Add epics to tool
description: As a user, I want the flexibility to add epics so that i can group the stories that deliver value together.

subject: Add themes to tool
description: As a user, I want to add themes to tools so that I can group set of related stories, using different tags.

subject: Add happiness to task
description: As a user, i want the flexibility to add the happiness to the task, such that team would know the happiness of working on the task.

subject: Create custom status states to user stories and tasks
description: As a user, I want to create or edit the existing status states so that I can make the status meaningful and understandable

subject: Indicating the status of sprint planning
description: As a user, i want to know the status of the sprint planning whether it is complete or not

subject: Indicating the status of sprint review and sprint goals
description: As a user, i want to know the status of the sprint review and whether the sprint goals are achieved or not.

subject: Create burndown charts for story points vs business value
description: As a user, I want to see the burn down chart for story points vs business value so that I can estimate the progress of project

subject: Ability to conduct retrospectives
description: As a user, i want to know what went well  to appreciate the team members and what didn't in the entire sprint to make sure the same problems wont repeat again.

subject: Read default configuration from a json file
description: As a user, I want to read default configuration from a json file so that I can set default values Ex. start date, sprint length

subject: Import details from taiga using API
description: As a user, I want to import all details from taiga using taiga API so that I see or make use of those in my tool

subject: Export information from tool to Taiga
description: As a user, I want to export projects and related information to taiga using API so that I can see the project details in Taiga as well.

subject: Add a step to input GitHub URL to project information
description: As a user, I want to add GitHub Url to project information so that it could see it in the information whenever need

subject: Add a step to input team details to project info
description: As a user, I want to add team members' information to the project information so that it will be on records and I can see it whenever needed.
